Love is patient and kind; love is notjealous or conceited or proud; love
isnot ill-mannered, or selfish or irritable;love does not keep a record of
wrongs.Love is not happy with evil, but ishappy with the truth. Love never
givesupï¼š its faith, hope and patience neverfail. Love is eternal.
